{"tid":2001632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳松青，一個熟悉嘅名；一單香港名案！有種既視感嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-04T16:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T17:59:22.000Z","uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7b73cd792a4e8e1f2dbd15cfa21a7278e05173","tid":2001632,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">佳寧案</span>歷時十七年，涉及款項達六十六億元，訴訟費更超過兩億元！但主謀陳松青只被判入獄三年，其中一年多更在羈留病房中渡過！不過，三個和案件有密切關係人士卻離奇死亡！其一是<span style=\"color: red;\">律師溫樹寶</span>，他被發現在寓所泳池溺斃，最後證實是自殺。另一名是<span style=\"color: red;\">法官柏嘉</span>，他於審結陳松青等人後一年，於塞浦路斯發生交通意外不治斃命；柏嘉太太於93年亦宣告破產。最令人印象深刻的是<span style=\"color: red;\">大馬裕民財務的財務總監伊巴謙</span>。1983年，他專責到港查核該公司一筆為數四十億元貸款，其後他的屍首被發現棄置於 大埔火車站 附近的蕉林內，警方相信他是遭人勒死 ！<br />\n<br />\n中共同香港政府玩佳寧案2.0？"},{"pid":"153f5f3b01fcc3630498a8bbc4f2c084e6684f10","tid":2001632,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"8b968c4ef52ef14580c0ff58d0718014ff91e96c","tid":2001632,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"佢係地政處處長？"},{"pid":"99e73336d370e082f660fd825230da01a2ebe685","tid":2001632,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2405f693bb1ac61c052dace59c7a0dd0b0e0f2c3","tid":2001632,"uid":80484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"咁癲 留名"},{"pid":"4d3902de07c2646c4461fb51b30293195bfc41eb","tid":2001632,"uid":75196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b968c4ef52ef14580c0ff58d0718014ff91e96c","tid":2001632,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"佢係地政處處長？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"同名同姓而已"},{"pid":"07f2e4e